| **PR count cap** | **`pr-breakdown`** lists **1‚Äì6** PR rows. **> 6** PRs or multi-initiative scope ‚Üí use **`plan and deliver`**. |
| **Implementation / ship** | **`coding-session`** and detached ship chain unchanged ‚Äî same skills and gates as plan-and-deliver. |
| **Command phrase** | **`plan and deliver a single phase`** only (see **`mission.yaml`**). |

Skill paths reuse [`.sedea/centers/research-and-development/missions/plan-and-deliver/skills/`](.sedea/centers/research-and-development/missions/plan-and-deliver/skills/) unless this mission later adds mission-local copies.

